OL,3,CCuts to mental health services
OL,4,C'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FGranada Reports journalist Anna
OL,7,FYoussef reports on why staff are
OL,8,Ftaking strike action
OL,10,FA group of mental health workers say
OL,11,Fthey have been forced to take strike
OL,12,Faction because poor staffing levels
OL,13,Fand a lack of funding is putting live
OL,14,Fat risk.
OL,16,FUnion members in the Early
OL,17,FIntervention in Psychosis teams across
OL,18,FGreater Manchester walked out for 24
OL,19,Fhours on Wednesday, 16 October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
