OL,3,CCuts to mental health services
OL,4,C'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,F"I am delighted that early
OL,7,Fintervention workers are striking",
OL,8,Fshe said. "I think its really
OL,9,Fimportant for people to remember that
OL,10,Fthis is not about pay.
OL,12,F"They're not asking for things for
OL,13,Fthemselves. They're saying that this
OL,14,Fservice is unsafe and it's absolutely
OL,15,Fimperative that this situation changes
OL,16,Fbefore the crisis gets any worse."
OL,18,FThe early-intervention workers,
OL,19,Femployed by Greater Manchester Mental
OL,20,FHealth NHS Foundation Trust (GMMH),
OL,21,Fare represented by UNISON and Unite.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
