OL,3,CCuts to mental health services
OL,4,C'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FThe unions say they are taking action
OL,7,Fover what they claim is the Trust's
OL,8,Ffailure to improve staffing levels,
OL,9,Fdespite its previous commitment to
OL,10,Fseek new funding to address this.
OL,12,FA recent freedom of information (FOI)
OL,13,Frequest revealed the North West's NHS
OL,14,Fhospital trusts spent #45m more on
OL,15,Fprivate mental health care beds in the
OL,16,Fpast three years.
OL,18,FSenior staff have recently said that
OL,19,Fthe service is "on its knees" and
OL,20,Flives are being put at risk.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
