OL,6,FThe additional stress on medical staff
OL,7,Fis putting a further strain on
OL,8,Fresources.
OL,10,FFormer mental health nurse Karen
OL,11,FReissmann joined the picket, and said
OL,12,Fher friends still in the system say
OL,13,Fthe situation is showing no signs of
OL,14,Fimprovement.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
