OL,3,CCuts to mental health services
OL,4,C'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FDr. John Mulligan, a clinical
OL,7,Fpsychologist and a representative for
OL,8,FUNITE the Union, says action is
OL,9,Fessential now to prevent more
OL,10,Favoidable deaths in Greater Manchester.
OL,12,F"What we believe its going to take to
OL,13,Ffix it is a large amount of immediate
OL,14,Finvestment into the locality," he
OL,15,Fexplains.
OL,17,F"Manchester is the poor cousin of
OL,18,FEngland, and early intervention and
OL,19,Fsecondary care services in Manchester
OL,20,Fare the poor cousins in Greater
OL,21,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
