OL,3,CCuts to mental health services
OL,4,C'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,F"We desperately need funding, we
OL,7,Fdesperately need more staff to be able
OL,8,Fto do the preventative work that we
OL,9,Fwant to do.
OL,11,F"We're caught in a vicious circle at
OL,12,Fthe moment, where the very limited
OL,13,Famount of money that we get in
OL,14,FManchester is split up between very
OL,15,Fneedy and important stuff, and there's
OL,16,Fnone left in the pot when it comes to
OL,17,Fpreventative services like ourselves."
OL,19,FAccording to Professor Anandi
OL,20,FRamamurthy additional cash is not the
OL,21,Fonly answer to the problem.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
