OL,3,CCuts to mental health services
OL,4,C'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FShe feels that a total rethink of how
OL,7,Fthe system works is needed: "Mental
OL,8,FHealth services definitely need more
OL,9,Ffunding, but they need more than more
OL,10,Ffunding.
OL,12,F"They need restructuring, we need a
OL,13,Fcompassionate system, a compassionate
OL,14,Fculture in society or we are going to
OL,15,Fsee more and more people in crisis."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
